name: ACQUA DI GIÃ’ POUR HOMME
description: A fragrance of contrasting sensations, opening with a splash of freshness like a powerful sea breeze that subsides into very natural harmony. Energising, and stimulating, it expresses healthy sensuality; an authentic and serene virility. Its complexity, however, suggests a subtle personality, full of nuance. The fragrant trail is particularly lasting and memorable.
